21:10.370 --> 21:12.939
'Cause it's so nice to get
the kids outside, playing...

21:12.972 --> 21:14.307
Oh, I wish.
Elijah has allergies.

21:15.475 --> 21:17.076
Could we come to your place?

21:17.109 --> 21:19.045
Why not?

21:19.078 --> 21:20.079
LATIN LOVER NARRATOR:
Because you don't live there.

21:20.112 --> 21:21.881
Uh, they will follow me home,

21:21.914 --> 21:23.950
and we'll meet you there.

21:23.983 --> 21:25.585
Okay, great.

21:27.420 --> 21:30.723
Now, Mateo,
where did you put that thermos?

21:31.891 --> 21:33.526
XIOMARA:
I'm hurrying.

21:33.560 --> 21:35.395
Where are you?
RAFAEL:
I'm here.

21:35.428 --> 21:36.463
What do you
want me to do

21:36.496 --> 21:37.730
