22:48.701 --> 22:49.969
Because I live here.

22:50.002 --> 22:51.638
Uh, that's right, you do, Mateo.

22:51.671 --> 22:53.773
Please come in.

23:01.113 --> 23:03.015
LATIN LOVER NARRATOR:
Ah, yes, the playdate.

23:03.049 --> 23:05.184
