since I lied so good?

27:39.926 --> 27:43.295
Mateo, you weren't lying, we
were playing a game, remember?

27:43.329 --> 27:45.197
A lying game.

27:45.231 --> 27:47.834
Next time Elijah comes over,
do we lie again?

27:54.340 --> 27:55.742
JANE:
So, Mateo, you were right.

27:55.775 --> 27:57.143
We did ask you to lie.

27:57.176 --> 28:00.046
How come?
I thought lying was wrong.

28:00.079 --> 28:01.380
It is.

28:01.413 --> 28:02.782
Most of the time.

28:02.815 --> 28:06.385
But other times,
we make a choice,

28:06.418 --> 28:09.756
and we weigh the cost of the lie
with the benefit of the lie.

28:09.789 --> 28:11.758
I don't understand.

28:15.928 --> 28:18.898
We're pretending to live
at Papa and Abuela's house

28:18.931 --> 28:20.867
so you're allowed to go
to your new school.

28:20.900 --> 28:22.802
RAFAEL: You see,
the school in our neighborhood

28:22.835 --> 28:23.870
isn't very good.

28:23.903 --> 28:25.404
Which isn't fair,

28:25.437 --> 28:27.373
but it's also life.

28:27.406 --> 28:29.909
So we're trying,
in just this one case,

28:29.942 --> 28:31.911
to make things
a little more fair.

28:31.944 --> 28:35.081
And in order to do that,
we pretend to live here.

28:35.114 --> 28:36.816
Well, what if I get mixed up?

28:36.849 --> 28:38.350
Or I forget?

28:38.384 --> 28:40.920
Hey.

28:40.953 --> 28:42.855
Buddy,
you can do this.

28:42.889 --> 28:44.323
You're a big boy.

28:44.356 --> 28:46.859
I'm scared.

28:46.893 --> 28:49.962
They're probably not even
gonna ask, Mr. Sweetface.

28:56.803 --> 28:58.170
Oh, yeah.

28:58.204 --> 29:00.172
And I actually had
my own breakthrough.

29:00.206 --> 29:01.507
Oh.

29:01.540 --> 29:04.510
About Dad and the Madame
Alexander doll he got me

29:04.543 --> 29:07.046
and how much I missed him.

29:09.982 --> 29:13.886
Yeah, but, I mean,
I missed him when he was alive.

29:13.920 --> 29:15.754
H-He was gone so much.

29:17.556 --> 29:19.225
I know, but...

29:26.899 --> 29:28.534
Wha...?

29:32.872 --> 29:36.275
Uh, but, Mom, of course
I was so grateful to him.

29:36.308 --> 29:37.844
But thinking back,

29:37.877 --> 29:40.512
what I wanted more than the doll

29:40.546 --> 29:42.014
was time with him.

29:47.854 --> 29:48.554
It's not a criticism,
I'm just...

29:53.025 --> 29:54.526
Oh, wha...

29:58.931 --> 30:00.967
XIOMARA:
She was so pissed.

30:01.000 --> 30:02.869
She just shut down.

30:02.902 --> 30:04.837
Clearly, she has
underlying issues

30:04.871 --> 30:07.573
from her own dysfunctional
relationship with her parents.

30:07.606 --> 30:09.475
What were they like?

30:09.508 --> 30:12.178
Well, they weren't exactly
her favorite topic.

30:12.211 --> 30:14.380
LATIN LOVER NARRATOR:
And, friends, that night,

30:14.413 --> 30:16.182
our porn stars talked.

30:16.215 --> 30:18.417
And I think I was scared
of what my mother would say

30:18.450 --> 30:20.319
if she knew about
your pregnancy.

30:20.352 --> 30:22.254
And that's another reason
I didn't reach out to you.

30:22.288 --> 30:24.190
And talked.

30:24.223 --> 30:27.059
I think that's why my reaction
was so big when you told me.

30:27.093 --> 30:29.095
On some level, all these years

30:29.128 --> 30:30.496
I've been projecting my anger

30:30.529 --> 30:32.198
at my absentee dad on you.

30:32.231 --> 30:33.866
And talked.

30:33.900 --> 30:37.003
That's probably why
I'm such a good actor.

30:37.036 --> 30:38.237
And talked.

30:38.270 --> 30:41.073
Ooh.

30:41.107 --> 30:42.909
I'm a little tipsy.

30:42.942 --> 30:46.212
Forget Drunk History...

30:46.245 --> 30:48.948
Stain all the
carpets you want,

30:48.981 --> 30:51.583
I love you so much,
Xiomara.

30:51.617 --> 30:54.453
I love you so much, too.

30:57.456 --> 31:00.960
LATIN LOVER NARRATOR:
And, friends, that night

31:00.993 --> 31:04.263
was the most romantic night
of their lives.

31:04.296 --> 31:06.465
They even made
another triptych.

31:06.498 --> 31:09.335
Not that one, obviously.

31:10.970 --> 31:13.105
How's Mateo?

31:13.139 --> 31:14.907
Um, he's asleep.

31:14.941 --> 31:17.176
Good.
How'd he seem?

31:17.209 --> 31:21.013
Not as scared, but he definitely
has more questions.

31:26.085 --> 31:30.156
Oh, I forgot my...

31:30.189 --> 31:32.058
brush.

32:06.292 --> 32:08.394
I couldn't sleep.

32:08.427 --> 32:12.264
Yeah, me either.

32:12.298 --> 32:14.600
I don't think I realized
what it would feel like.

32:14.633 --> 32:16.168
Having to explain to a kid

32:16.202 --> 32:19.738
all these different
levels and layers to lying?

32:19.771 --> 32:22.174
Yeah.

32:22.208 --> 32:23.342
It's hard.

32:23.375 --> 32:25.744
And there's a lot
at stake.

32:25.777 --> 32:27.279
And we have to be
on the same page

32:27.313 --> 32:30.582
and focus on co-parenting.

32:30.616 --> 32:33.319
I agree.

32:33.352 --> 32:35.154
That's why
I'm moving out.

32:36.688 --> 32:38.290
I'm gonna move in
with Petra.

32:38.324 --> 32:40.592
Just until Luisa's better
and we sort things out.

32:40.626 --> 32:41.994
You don't have to move out.

32:42.028 --> 32:43.295
I do.

32:43.329 --> 32:47.066
Because if I'm being honest,

32:47.099 --> 32:49.501
part of the reason
I was staying was for you.

32:49.535 --> 32:52.671
You asked me if I'll
be able to let go,

32:52.704 --> 32:55.107
and I said yes.

32:55.141 --> 32:58.010
And I will,
but it's gonna be hard

32:58.044 --> 33:01.313
because it means letting go
of something pretty big--

33:01.347 --> 33:03.615
the possibility of us.

33:03.649 --> 33:06.018
Which has been there for me
in the back of my mind

33:06.052 --> 33:07.786
for a long time.

33:07.819 --> 33:12.391
And I just don't think
I can let that go

33:12.424 --> 33:14.293
living here with you.

33:17.396 --> 33:22.134
Me, too, but...
this is best.

33:22.168 --> 33:25.304
It's just hard to...

33:25.337 --> 33:28.207
give up the idea
that something perfect

33:28.240 --> 33:30.676
might not have been
perfect for everyone.

33:34.780 --> 33:39.285
That was about you and Xo.

33:39.318 --> 33:41.820
I heard you last night.

33:41.853 --> 33:44.623
You had one experience,
and she had another.

33:44.656 --> 33:47.126
Which may or may not
have been

33:47.159 --> 33:50.062
similar to what happened
with me and...

33:50.096 --> 33:52.564
she who will not be named.

33:54.833 --> 33:56.435
Rafael Solano?
That's me.

33:56.468 --> 33:58.237
Thanks.

34:03.775 --> 34:06.445
It's from my sister.

34:06.478 --> 34:08.247
This is my third message.

34:08.280 --> 34:09.515
Please have Ms. Ramos
call me back.

34:10.849 --> 34:12.351
You scared me.

34:14.120 --> 34:15.487
Let me know
what you think.

34:15.521 --> 34:18.157
Go ahead, read it.

34:20.392 --> 34:21.727
"Dear Rafael,

34:21.760 --> 34:23.595
"It's been a week.
Finally I feel ready

34:23.629 --> 34:26.232
to write to you and tell you
what I think of what you did."

34:26.265 --> 34:28.200
Keep going.

34:28.234 --> 34:30.669
"I know now that Carl was real.

34:30.702 --> 34:33.572
"Anezka told me.
She told me everything--

34:33.605 --> 34:36.375
how you set me up to get your
inheritance back"

34:36.408 --> 34:39.245
Stop lying.

34:39.278 --> 34:41.680
I just went to the hospital,
and guess what.

34:41.713 --> 34:43.282
After Luisa checked herself out,

34:43.315 --> 34:44.450
a woman named Krishna showed up

34:44.483 --> 34:45.684
asking all kinds of questions.

34:45.717 --> 34:47.719
Even tried to bribe the staff

34:47.753 --> 34:49.721
for information
on Luisa's whereabouts.

34:49.755 --> 34:51.723
Krishna?
Well, she's fired, obviously.

34:51.757 --> 34:53.125
Stop, just stop!

34:53.159 --> 34:55.727
Tell me the truth.

35:05.304 --> 35:09.775
My mother and sister
set everyone up.

35:09.808 --> 35:12.778
They hired Carl to make Luisa
think she was crazy.

35:12.811 --> 35:15.447
I sent Krishna
to find Luisa

35:15.481 --> 35:17.183
as soon as I knew
Anezka said you did it.

35:17.216 --> 35:19.251
How long did you know
Carl was real?

35:19.285 --> 35:22.154
I was going to tell
you and Luisa

35:22.188 --> 35:23.255
just as soon as I dealt with
my mother and Anezka.

35:23.289 --> 35:24.690
How long, Petra?

35:24.723 --> 35:26.792
How long did you leave
my sister in an institution

35:26.825 --> 35:29.228
knowing she wasn't
hallucinating?

35:29.261 --> 35:31.430
A week.

35:45.311 --> 35:46.645
I can't believe Petra
didn't tell you.

35:46.678 --> 35:47.746
I know.

35:47.779 --> 35:50.882
And I need to be
done with that.

35:50.916 --> 35:52.318
With all the lying.

35:52.351 --> 35:55.221
Which is why I don't
want Mateo lying

35:55.254 --> 35:56.655
about his school.

35:56.688 --> 35:58.824
What? No, that
isn't fair.
Okay.
Okay, hold on...

35:58.857 --> 36:01.193
Now, we made this decision, and
I get that you're suddenly...
Hold on.

36:01.227 --> 36:03.562
So I found
a studio apartment

36:03.595 --> 36:04.796
in your parents'
school district,

36:04.830 --> 36:06.465
and I just signed the lease.

36:06.498 --> 36:08.667
What?

36:08.700 --> 36:11.703
Sold my car.
Paid through the ear.

36:11.737 --> 36:13.205
Oh...

36:13.239 --> 36:17.309
I'll take the bus to work
or... carpool with you?

36:17.343 --> 36:20.412
You can totally
carpool with me.

36:20.446 --> 36:21.980
You got an apartment?

36:22.013 --> 36:24.950
Don't get too excited,
it's super small.

36:24.983 --> 36:26.918
I didn't even know
they made them that small.

36:26.952 --> 36:32.591
It sounds... amazing.

36:32.624 --> 36:34.293
LATIN LOVER NARRATOR:
And speaking of amazing...

36:37.929 --> 36:40.499
And cut. Moving on
to the last setup.

36:40.532 --> 36:42.268
Give me Baby.

36:42.301 --> 36:44.403
I want time with her
while they light.

36:47.806 --> 36:49.308
ALBA:
Xiomara?

36:49.341 --> 36:50.542
Hey, what are you
doing here?

37:06.392 --> 37:09.528
Ma, no.

37:09.561 --> 37:10.996
I shouldn't have
said that to you.

37:11.029 --> 37:12.331
I get it.
No, no, no.

37:33.352 --> 37:35.020
EXECUTIVE:
So, as we close out
this journey,

37:35.053 --> 37:38.657
I just want to thank you all
for your devotion to Guillermo

37:38.690 --> 37:41.327
and for...
I got the rewrite.

37:41.360 --> 37:44.062
I saw you crush me like
a bug once you grow big.

37:44.095 --> 37:47.032
And we are officially
announcing a sequel.

37:51.370 --> 37:53.505
Rogelio, do you want
to say a few words?

37:53.539 --> 37:55.040
LATIN LOVER NARRATOR:
And in that moment,

37:55.073 --> 37:56.875
with Alba's words
ringing in his ears,

37:56.908 --> 38:00.379
Rogelio realized
he had to be a bigger man.

38:00.412 --> 38:02.080
But not a giant.

38:02.113 --> 38:04.383
Drop everything.
We need an emergency rewrite.

38:05.584 --> 38:08.487
A baby needs her father,

38:08.520 --> 38:09.721
which is why

38:09.755 --> 38:11.289
I will take the next year off.

38:12.491 --> 38:13.825
Esteban will be your lead.

38:14.760 --> 38:15.961
And I will be

38:15.994 --> 38:17.596
your hero.

38:21.867 --> 38:24.570
PETRA:
Thank you.

38:24.603 --> 38:27.473
For... coming back.

38:27.506 --> 38:30.909
L-Look, you were right
about everything.

38:30.942 --> 38:32.678
The police came for my e-mails,

38:32.711 --> 38:34.946
my phone records, my time cards.

38:34.980 --> 38:37.416
And I don't need someone who's
gonna blow smoke up my ass.

38:37.449 --> 38:39.050
I need someone to make sure
I don't go to jail

38:39.084 --> 38:40.051
for protecting myself.

38:40.085 --> 38:42.921
You accused me of being a crook.

38:42.954 --> 38:45.424
And I am so sorry.

38:45.457 --> 38:47.626
Look...

38:47.659 --> 38:51.062
I know this
is not an excuse, but...

38:53.465 --> 38:56.134
...this is obviously
a very emotional time for me.

38:56.167 --> 38:57.969
My sister's dead,

38:58.003 --> 39:00.706
my hotel is in limbo, and...

39:00.739 --> 39:03.409
I-I don't have anyone

39:03.442 --> 39:04.876
on my side anymore.

39:04.910 --> 39:06.878
I had my ex in my corner,

39:06.912 --> 39:08.647
but I went
and ruined that, so...

39:08.680 --> 39:11.617
And now I'm all alone.

39:13.619 --> 39:15.887
What, do you get
some sick pleasure

39:15.921 --> 39:18.390
in other people's pain?
Keep wearing your heart
on your sleeve.

39:18.424 --> 39:21.092
It makes you a much more
sympathetic defendant.

39:21.126 --> 39:23.161
If you become a defendant,

39:23.194 --> 39:26.498
which I will work hard
to ensure that you don't.

39:30.502 --> 39:33.171
LATIN LOVER NARRATOR:
Aw, look, Petra made a friend.

39:33.204 --> 39:35.140
Thank you.

39:35.173 --> 39:37.175
A friend who charges
$600 an hour,

39:37.208 --> 39:38.644
but still.

39:38.677 --> 39:41.012
I'd almost say
things are looking up.

39:42.648 --> 39:45.451
Okay, I'm her lawyer.

39:45.484 --> 39:47.486
What's next?

39:47.519 --> 39:49.087
There is no next.

39:49.120 --> 39:51.189
That's all the pictures.
It's just one room.

39:51.222 --> 39:53.592
Well, it's great.

39:53.625 --> 39:55.093
It will be great.

39:55.126 --> 39:57.729
We'll decorate it on
the cheap. I'm a pro.

39:57.763 --> 39:59.565
I'm looking forward to it.

39:59.598 --> 40:00.899
Me, too.

40:00.932 --> 40:03.435
Okay.
Hmm.

40:03.469 --> 40:05.637
Let me just ask.
Oh, please, don't let this

40:05.671 --> 40:08.640
be about the kiss.
Do you really not think
we have chemistry anymore?

40:08.674 --> 40:10.676
I don't know.
That's what you're saying.

40:10.709 --> 40:12.478
Okay, fine. You know what?

40:12.511 --> 40:13.745
Kiss me again.

40:13.779 --> 40:15.581
Are you serious?

40:15.614 --> 40:17.215
Let's do it. Go.

40:17.248 --> 40:19.685
Okay.

40:21.687 --> 40:23.589
Okay. Wow.

40:23.622 --> 40:26.758
Sorry. Okay. No.
You are obviously not
in the right headspace again.

40:26.792 --> 40:28.960
I'm fine. I'm ready.

40:28.994 --> 40:31.830
No, I don't want to anymore.
It is now or never.

40:31.863 --> 40:33.732
This is your window.

40:35.734 --> 40:37.235
Okay.
Mm-hmm.

40:37.268 --> 40:39.638
Fine. Fine.

40:39.671 --> 40:41.807
Mm-hmm.
But first,

40:41.840 --> 40:43.208
you have to think
about what comes next.

40:43.241 --> 40:44.643
I've thought
everything through.
No.

40:45.877 --> 40:49.214
What I would do

40:49.247 --> 40:51.550
after we kiss.

40:51.583 --> 40:53.184
What do you mean?

40:53.218 --> 40:55.687
Like where I would put my...

40:55.721 --> 40:58.557
hand, for instance.

40:58.590 --> 41:00.225
Oh?

41:00.258 --> 41:04.062
And my... tongue.

41:04.095 --> 41:06.798
Where are you gonna put it?

41:08.834 --> 41:11.603
Oh, wow.

41:11.637 --> 41:14.272
That's just to start.

41:14.305 --> 41:16.808
Then I'd...

41:20.979 --> 41:22.981
Okay, kiss me now.

41:29.320 --> 41:31.222
Eh.

41:37.629 --> 41:41.299
LATIN LOVER NARRATOR:
And, friends, what can I say?

41:41.332 --> 41:42.801
It felt like

41:42.834 --> 41:44.803
a telenovela.

41:53.211 --> 41:54.646
MATEO:
Yay!

41:54.680 --> 41:56.281
You guys are kissing!

41:56.314 --> 41:58.316
Does that mean
you're getting married?

